TinyLaF 1.4.0

API specification for the Tiny Look and Feel, version 1.4.0.

Packages
de.muntjak.tinylookandfeel This package contains classes related to Theme Switching (see class Theme), class TinyTableHeaderUI supports Sortable Table Data.
de.muntjak.tinylookandfeel.table This package contains SortableTableData, the interface all sortable table models must implement.

 

API specification for the Tiny Look and Feel, version 1.4.0. Documentation is provided only for a small subset of classes, related to theme switching and to TinyLaF's sortable table data.
